About

A brief introduction of myself

Hello, my name is Jan Michael Laranjo as you can tell from the title, but everyone calls me Jan. I am master CS student at the University of Technologies Vienna. Currently I am working for s IT Solutions as a student developer in the finance industry.

In my spare time I spend my time with my beloved fiance. We like to travel and love food. Sports is also another passion, especially hiking. I also love to listen to audio books about personal development. Furthermore I like to broaden my knowledge by reading books.
